                    &lt;div class=&quot;flex--item mb0 mt4&quot;&gt;
                        &lt;a href=&quot;/questions/203198/event-binding-on-dynamically-created-elements&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Event binding on dynamically created elements?&lt;/a&gt;
